social_posts.post_text:
keeping traditions 🎄 Our love has gotten us through the unthinkable.  Even through our grief, this year will forever be the most special to me, all of our memories we’ve made, traditions we’ve kept and how close we have gotten as a family. 

I love you girls more than you could possibly imagine.

One. You would’ve been one. My bean. My second baby girl. Happy birthday in the spirit world my beautiful little soul 

Today at 9:43am you were born 7lbs 3oz 21in • and we will celebrate you every year until I can finally hold you in my arms again

Every second of every day I search for you and I know you’re with me as my guide, but it’s not enough today. The what ifs have consumed my mind and I don’t even know how it’s possible to cry this much or how it’s possible an entire year has already passed without you

I’ll love you forever my littlest love. I wish you were here 🤍

Briar Rose Fazzino || 6lbs 7oz 20 in ||born at 8:52am on 1/20/23 💕🌈 our official rainbow baby girl 

She has been our families best kept secret thus far. After losing our Bean last year we fell into grief so hard we never thought we would pull out of it. We struggled with how to heal and find our way to our new normal. And then one day Heather came to me and told me she wanted to do a retrieval and try to get pregnant. Something she’s never wanted to do ever.  1 successful round of IVF later we had a BFP and then started the journey 

Beans passing left us both forever changed and all her spirit has done is brought happiness for us in her own ways. Her spirit brought us Briar. And heathers body brought us Briar. And my love will raise Briar as my 3rd daughter. Freya’s little sister. My littlest baby girl. 

Heather, I can never thank you enough for the physical  sacrifice you have made for our family. You were hysterical, positive and so brave the entire time, I have never loved you so much. All I could do was cry on your face in the operating room and say “you did it babe” - thank you for bringing us the rainbow after the storm 

Freya, Bean, Briar and I love you more than you could ever imagine 🤍🌈💕

Baby Briar - my rainbow baby, I promise you i will be your rock, your best friend and anything else I can do for you and your sister as your Mommy.  I knew I loved you before I met you and my heart is gushing for you

Here we go. Welcome to the family little girl! 🌈💕

We think Freya is loving her position as big sister. She’s waited for this moment just as long as we have 💕🌈
#rainbowbaby #sisters #bigsis #littlesis

2 weeks of loving you 💕🌈 our littlest love. 

Baby Briar you’re so loved already, it’s insane how much healing you’ve brought to our family. There’s warmth again, there’s laughter and peace. 

I’ll love you forever rainbow 🤍

my littlest valentines • my heart is so full this year ❤️🤍

Freya and Briar you girls are my world and I am so lucky every single day to be your mommy. I love you today and every day

#foreverfazzino #lgbtqfamily #valentinesday #girlfam

With all the heartbreak we’ve gone through, you two bring so much light into our lives. Keep snuggling and loving each other as much as we love you. 

You girls are so special to us, we cherish every second with you 🌈💕

Also briar was much less terrified than she looked 🤣

motherhood is priceless and your babies growing is so bittersweet 
#motherhood #girlmomlife #growingbabies

All of my babies. My Freya, My Briar and my angel baby bean 🤍 

thank you @stefaniecolephotography for bringing all of my children together for the picture I thought I would never get, and even though it’s not the picture I planned, it’s perfect.

I know you, I walked with you once upon a dream. I know you the gleam in your eyes is so familiar a gleam. Yet I know it’s true that visions are seldom all they seem. But if I know you I know what you’ll do, you’ll love me at once the way you did once, upon on a dream. 
…
…….
……….
our rainbow, our sweet briar rose. We love you so. I love you most. 

#rainbowbaby #twomoms #samesexparents #babygirl #loveafterloss

Life is S W E E T with Briar Rose 🌹

This day was so magical celebrating our rainbow.  Our family and friends coming together with their families meant the world to us. 

It was the celebration we’ve been waiting to have for a long time. Briar you were so worth the wait. Thank you to everyone who came it warmed our hearts. 

Decor : @design_your_day_events 
Florals: @stellasflowerbar 
Rentals: @elitetentpartyrental 
Playscape: @partyfiestany 
Extra yummies: @dolcebellany 

#sipandseeparty #meetthebaby #briarrose #foreverfazzino #lgbtqiafamily

The next generation of love, holidays and being obsessed with each other 

My Baby Dominic muffin man your Baptism was beautiful and I am beyond honored to have been asked to be your Godmother and guide you through this life. Nothing and no one will ever change my love for you💙 good luck to anyone who tries to hurt you between me and your mommy lol. I love you so much handsome

Screaming Happy 33rd Birthday to my Love • I can’t believe I’ve celebrated 10 trips around the sun with you already. 

It literally feels like yesterday that we met and now look at the family we’ve built together. I love tea and cookies with you, fighting with you, how we always challenge each other and learning from you but most of all I love the way you love me🤍 you really are the best, even though I refuse to not be hard on you some days because when you’re 20 I’ll always be your 80. 

 I can never thank you enough for transforming and pushing yourself to be the person I always knew you could be. That’s what makes me love you the most - it’s so rewarding as a partner to see you thrive in what you love  and that our girls get to experience so much because of you.  It’s so funny that you’re actually the calm one now but you protect us so fiercely at the same time. Our girls are learning they are so lucky to have you, that which I already know. There’s so much I can write about because I truly love our life together and all the memories we’ve made.  But there’s so many more for us to make. 

There is literally nothing we can’t face and conqueror when we’re together. Except laundry. I just can’t even with you lmfao 

We’re all so proud to call you ours🤍
I can’t wait to see you as king triton for Halloween because that’s what Freya wants 🤣

Baby bean is with you always, she’ll make today extra special for you 

We love you birthday girl ! 
Love Mommy, Freya, Bean, and Briar 
And our hoard of animals 

#foreverfazzino #lovealwayswins

🤍 B I G SIS •  L I T T L E SIS 🤍 

You two are the best and I never imagined I could love you both the way I do.  #foreverfazzino #lgbtqfamily

Can you tell me how to get? 
how to get to SESAME STREET ☀️

We literally had the best day at @sesameplace . We got to meet all the characters, watch the parade, splash around the water park and of course came home with everything Abby and Elmo • we can’t wait to go back! 

#sesameplace #sesamestreet #foreverfazzino #girlfam #twomoms

Having daughters is the greatest gift by far that I have ever received. It comes with such great responsibly. 

I celebrate all three of my daughters - my sun, my moon and my stars. 

You have my entire heart #girlmom

Freya girl turned F O U R 🐻🎀

My heart exploded and broke at the same time on your birthday. I cried when I put you to bed because I looked in to a room with a big bed and my not so little baby. 

One day you’ll see just how much you mean to me. I’m so proud to be your mother. I’m proud that you stand up for yourself, that your sensitive and care about others feels, I’m proud that you’re so smart and so much more.  You truly have changed my soul and I can’t even begin to explain how you’ve made me whole. I love you more than words could say, baby of mine. 

This day was more than a birthday - it was a celebration of the beautiful soul that you are - building bears, bounce house fun, and the most yummy sweet treats- it was a perfect day that not even the rain could stop! 

Thank you @design_your_day_events , @funstuffexpress  and @partyfiestany for making the day perfect

Happy gotcha day my Briar Rose! 

Adopting you today is one of the greatest honors in my life thus far. 

I absolutely love being your mother and I couldn’t imagine my life without you. Thank you to our amazing Adoption Attorney and our family for the love you brought to this incredible day

There are no words for how much the three of you mean to me.  Grateful doesn’t even cut it 

You’re the reason I’m able to get up in the mornings. Wipe my tears and get through the days that are the heaviest. 

Thank you for loving me the way you do 🤍

Fazzino Family Traditions 🎄
Year number 4 • First as a family of 4 • so many more to go

It’s the most wonderful time of the year 🎅🏼🎄

We’re counting down the days until Christmas ! And wishing everyone the happiest of holidays 

Love, 
The Fazzino Family 
And our cookie stealing elves
